<apex:page standardController="Booking__c" readOnly="advanced_pdf" applyHtmlTag="false" applyBodyTag="false" 
standardStylesheets="false" sidebar="false" showHeader="false" extensions="RefundletterExtension" cache="false"
 renderAs="advanced_pdf" docType="html-5.0">


<html>
    <head>
        <style>
       table, th, td {
      border: 0px solid black;
        }
        body {
              font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
              font-size: 11px;
            }
        </style>
        <style>
               @page
                {
                margin-top: 25%;
                margin-bottom: 10%;
                @top-center {
                content: element(header);
                }
                @bottom-center {
                content: element(footer);
                }
                @bottom-left {
                content: element(pagen);
                }  
                }
                div.header 
                {
                position: running(header);
                }
                div.footer 
                {
                position: running(footer);
                }
                .pagenumber:before 
                {
                content: counter(page);
                }
                .pagecount:before 
                {
                content: counter(pages);
                }
          
           .float-container {
            border: 3px solid #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            }

            .float-child1 {
                width: 5%;
                float: left;
                padding: 20px;
                border: 2px solid red;
            }  
             .float-child2 {
                width: 95%;
                float: left;
                padding: 20px;
                border: 2px solid red;
            } 
            </style>
    </head>
    <body>
      <div class="footer">
            <apex:image url="/sfc/servlet.shepherd/version/download/{!ProjectFooter}" width="700" height="50" />
          	<p style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:8px;text-align: center;"> Page <span class="pagenumber"/> of <span class="pagecount"/></p>
      </div>
      <div width = "100%" class="header" style="margin-top: 20px;margin-left: 10px;">
                <apex:image url="/sfc/servlet.shepherd/version/download/{!ProjectHeader}" width="700" height="140" />
      </div> 
   
    
    <div style="padding-left:0px;">
        <span style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;">
        <span style="text-align:left;">
            To,
        <span style="float:right;">
        Date:&nbsp;<apex:outputText style="text-align: right;" value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> 
        <apex:param value="{!TODAY()}" /></apex:outputText>
        </span>
        </span>
        <br/>
        {!booking.Primary_Applicant__r.Name}<br/>
        {!accountObject.PersonMailingStreet}, {!accountObject.PersonMailingCity},<br/>
        {!accountObject.PersonMailingState} - {!accountObject.PersonMailingPostalCode},<br/>
        {!accountObject.PersonMailingCountry}<br/>
        Mob No.: {!accountObject.PersonMobilePhone} 
        </span>
        </div><br/>      
           <div  style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;text-align: justify;">
           <center><b><u>Sub: Refund of balance amounts pertaining to Application/ Allotment in respect of said Apartment.</u></b><br/><br/></center>
           </div><br/>
            <div style="padding-left:0px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;text-align: justify;">
        <b>Re:</b> Your Cancellation Notice dated&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> 
        <apex:param value="{!booking.Cancel_or_Termination_date__c}" /></apex:outputText> in respect of Apartment No. {!sPropertyobj.Unit__r.name} on the {!sPropertyobj.Unit__r.Floor__c}<sup>{!floor}</sup> floor in
         {!booking.Project_Name__r.Name} {!if(LOWER(booking.Tower_Name__r.Name) == 'na',"",booking.Tower_Name__r.Name)} Project (“said Apartment”), situated at  {!project.City__c}, {!project.state__c} - {!project.Postal_Code__c}.
    </div>
    <p style="padding-left:0px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;">
    Dear {!accountObject.Salutation}  {!booking.Primary_Applicant__r.Name},</p>
     
    <ol type="1" style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;text-align: justify;">
        <li style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;margin-Bottom: 8px;">
            We refer to your cancellation request vide your Letter/ Email dated&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> 
        <apex:param value="{!booking.Cancel_or_Termination_date__c}" /></apex:outputText>&nbsp;(“Cancellation Notice”), requesting us, as a result of some personal
            reasons experienced at your end, to cancel your application/ allotment of the captioned Apartment under the Application Form dated&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> 
        <apex:param value="{!booking.Booking_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText>
            (“Form”)/ Agreement for Sale dated&nbsp;<apex:outputText rendered="{!if(booking.Registration_Status__c== 'Completed',true,false)}" value="{0,date,dd-MM-yyyy}">
              <apex:param value="{!booking.Registration_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText><apex:outputText rendered="{!if(booking.Registration_Status__c!= 'Completed',true,false)}" value="NA"></apex:outputText> registered vide No. {!if(booking.Registration_Number__c!=null,booking.Registration_Number__c,"NA")} (“Agreement”) (as the case may be) and all writings pursuant thereto.<br/>
        </li>
         <li style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;margin-Bottom: 8px;">
             We also refer to our reply dated&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> 
        <apex:param value="{!TODAY()}" /></apex:outputText>&nbsp;pursuant to your Cancellation Notice, whereby the said transaction with respect to the allotment 
             of the captioned Apartment was cancelled with immediate effect and agreed to refund the balance amounts, if any (“Refund Amounts”), 
             as per the provisions of the Form/Agreement, (as the case may be).
        </li>
         <li style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;margin-Bottom: 8px;">
            We have transferred/ refunded you the balance amounts (in accordance with but not limited to clause 8.8 of the Form and/or 
            clause 8(vi) of the Agreement, as the case may be) paid by you, being Rs. <apex:outputText value="{0, number, #,###.##}"><apex:param value="{!paymentObj.Amount__c}"/></apex:outputText>
             (Rupees {!AmountInWords} only) vide RTGS/ NEFT, as a mode
            of payment having UTR No./ Reference No. {!paymentObj.Cheque_Transaction_Number__c } dated&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> 
        <apex:param value="{!paymentObj.Payment_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText> to Bank Account No. {!project.Builder_Organization__r.Bank_Account_Number__c}.
        </li>
         <li style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;margin-Bottom: 8px;">
           We further inform you that as per the provisions of your Form/ Agreement, (as the case may be), you have ceased to have any right, title, 
           interest, claim or demand of any nature whatsoever either against the Promoter or in the said Apartment or any part 
           thereof or the Project and we are fully entitled to deal with the said Apartment as we may in our sole absolute and unfettered 
           discretion deem fit and proper, without any further recourse to you.
        </li>
         <li style="font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 11px;margin-Bottom: 8px;">
            We request you to confirm the receipt of the aforesaid and to confirm that you have no objection whatsoever in respect
            of the Form/ Agreement (as the case may be) and the contents hereof by countersigning this letter.
        </li>
    </ol>   
        <table width="100%" style="margin-top: 20px;padding-left:0px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:11px;">
		 <tr>
		 <td><p>Yours faithfully,
            <br/><br/><br/>
             {!project.Builder_Organization__r.name}</p></td>
		<td><p style="text-align:right;">I/ We received
            <br/><br/><br/>
             {!booking.Primary_Applicant__r.Name}</p></td>
		 </tr>
		 
		 </table>
    </body>
</html>
</apex:page>